channel.title: Models are Located in What Cache File?
channel.description:
Well, here's my question. I'm wondering, where are the models located in the RuneScape cache. I've heard it was [code] main_file_cache.idx1 [/code] But can anybody confirm?
And another thing, are the models found as .dat files or .mdl files in there?
Thanks.
